        "content": "<p>So I took a stab at this: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/pcwalton/status/1181394377081442304\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/pcwalton/status/1181394377081442304\">https://twitter.com/pcwalton/status/1181394377081442304</a></p>\n<div class=\"inline-preview-twitter\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/pcwalton/status/1181394377081442304\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"twitter-avatar\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/619088718/twitter-icon_normal.jpeg\"></a><p>Idea: The “left-pad index”, a score for Rust crates that combines small size with popularity.\n\nThe goal would be to find potential candidates for additions to the standard library, or at least merging into larger crates.</p><span>- Patrick Walton (@pcwalton)</span></div></div>",
        "id": 178310852,
        "sender_full_name": "Tony Arcieri",
        "timestamp": 1571247393
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>results: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bascule/status/1184523027888988160\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/bascule/status/1184523027888988160\">https://twitter.com/bascule/status/1184523027888988160</a></p>\n<div class=\"inline-preview-twitter\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/bascule/status/1184523027888988160\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"twitter-avatar\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/450061818606522368/pjDTHFB9_normal.jpeg\"></a><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/pcwalton\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/pcwalton\">@pcwalton</a> I took a stab at this, extracting info about the top 500 crates via the <a href=\"https://t.co/v0BPxyGjof\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://t.co/v0BPxyGjof\">http://crates.io</a> API, putting it into a spreadsheet, and dividing the number of recent downloads by the crate size. Here's the top 25 crates with the highest \"left-pad index\"\n<a href=\"https://t.co/NDBr3OnnGk\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://t.co/NDBr3OnnGk\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wwahRMHG3buvnfHjmPQFU4Kyfq15oTwbfsuZpwHUKc4/edit?usp=sharing</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/PJGTyNLBZl\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://t.co/PJGTyNLBZl\">https://twitter.com/bascule/status/1184523027888988160/photo/1</a></p><span>- Tony \"ABOLISH ICE\" Arcieri (@bascule)</span><div class=\"twitter-image\"><a href=\"https://t.co/PJGTyNLBZl\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://t.co/PJGTyNLBZl\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EHBFajWUYAEqiIX.jpg:thumb\"></a></div></div></div>",
